@startuml RAG问答核心链路
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 120

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端\n(React)" as Frontend
participant "ChatController" as Controller
participant "StreamChatPipeline" as Pipeline
participant "ConversationMemoryService" as Memory
participant "QueryRewriteService" as Rewrite
participant "IntentResolver" as Intent
participant "RetrievalEngine" as Retrieve
participant "MultiChannelRetrievalEngine" as MultiRetrieve
participant "McpToolExecutor" as Mcp
participant "LLMMcpParameterExtractor" as ParamExtract
participant "RAGPromptService" as Prompt
participant "RoutingLLMService" as LLM

User -> Frontend: 输入问题
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/ragent/rag/v3/chat (SSE)
Controller -> Pipeline: execute(ctx)

== 记忆与改写 ==
Pipeline -> Memory: loadAndAppend(conversationId, userId, question)
Memory --> Pipeline: history

Pipeline -> Rewrite: rewriteWithSplit(question, history)
Rewrite --> Pipeline: RewriteResult (rewrittenQuestion, subQuestions)

== 意图识别 ==
Pipeline -> Intent: resolve(rewriteResult)
Intent --> Pipeline: List<SubQuestionIntent> (nodeScores)

alt 意图置信度不足
    Pipeline -> Frontend: 生成歧义引导选项
    Frontend --> User: 请选择您想问的是...
end

== 检索 ==
Pipeline -> Retrieve: retrieve(subIntents, topK)

note over Retrieve, MultiRetrieve #FFFDE7: 以下两路检索并行执行\n(通过 ragContextExecutor 和 mcpBatchExecutor 线程池)

Retrieve -> MultiRetrieve: retrieveKnowledgeChannels(subIntents, topK)
MultiRetrieve --> Retrieve: List<RetrievedChunk>

loop for each MCP intent
    Retrieve -> ParamExtract: extractParameters(question, tool)
    ParamExtract -> ParamExtract: LLM 提取参数
    Retrieve -> Mcp: execute(params)
    Mcp --> Retrieve: CallToolResult
end

Retrieve --> Pipeline: RetrievalContext (kbContext, mcpContext, intentChunks)

alt 检索为空 && 非增强模式
    Pipeline -> Frontend: "未检索到与问题相关的文档内容。"
    Frontend --> User: 显示兜底消息
else 增强回答模式 (F-01)
    Pipeline -> Pipeline: 继续组装 Prompt，走增强模板
end

== Prompt 组装与生成 ==
Pipeline -> Prompt: buildStructuredMessages(context, history, question)
Prompt --> Pipeline: List<ChatMessage> (system + evidence + history + user)

Pipeline -> LLM: streamChat(chatRequest, callback)

loop SSE 流式输出
    LLM --> Frontend: onContent(delta)
    Frontend --> User: 实时渲染 Markdown
end

LLM --> Frontend: onComplete()
Frontend --> User: 回答完成

@enduml
